WEBVTT

00:12.751 --> 00:16.799
-♪ SOME PEOPLE STAND
IN THE DARKNESS ♪

00:16.929 --> 00:20.846
♪ AFRAID TO STEP
INTO THE LIGHT ♪

00:20.977 --> 00:24.372
♪ SOME PEOPLE NEED
TO HELP SOMEBODY ♪

00:24.502 --> 00:27.810
♪ WHEN THE EDGE OF
SURRENDER'S IN SIGHT ♪

00:27.940 --> 00:30.639
♪ DON'T YOU WORRY

00:31.292 --> 00:34.251
♪ IT'S GONNA BE ALRIGHT ♪

00:36.775 --> 00:38.560
♪ CAUSE I'M ALWAYS READY

00:38.690 --> 00:42.477
♪ I WON'T LET YOU
OUT OF MY SIGHT ♪

00:45.393 --> 00:49.440
♪ [I'LL BE READY]
I'LL BE READY ♪

00:49.571 --> 00:51.660
♪ NEVER YOU FEAR

00:51.790 --> 00:53.357
